listing.description:
# API Labz Trello-to-HubSpot Deal Creator

Transform your Trello cards into a powerful sales funnel by automatically creating HubSpot deals from your cards.

## How It Works:

**API Labz Authentication**
   
![](https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unlimited-apis.appspot.com/o/applicationFiles%2Flistings%2FTrello%20Powerups%2FHubSpot%2FHubspot1.gif?alt=media&token=9eba3f47-36af-467e-813c-9c7752cce27c)

**HubSpot Connection**
   
![](https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unlimited-apis.appspot.com/o/applicationFiles%2Flistings%2FTrello%20Powerups%2FHubSpot%2FHubSpot2.gif?alt=media&token=f8a0312f-e9e0-4402-91ba-dabeba96cb46)

**Configuration Setup**
   
![](https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unlimited-apis.appspot.com/o/applicationFiles%2Flistings%2FTrello%20Powerups%2FHubSpot%2FHubSpot3.gif?alt=media&token=fb077103-2c57-4d0b-85dc-a34cdf76f26b)

**Deal Creation**
   
![](https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unlimited-apis.appspot.com/o/applicationFiles%2Flistings%2FTrello%20Powerups%2FHubSpot%2FHubSpot4.gif?alt=media&token=0b79feea-7325-4d39-a8ee-dea3dde93d1e)

## Key Features:

- **Seamless Integration**: Connect your Trello and HubSpot accounts securely
- **Automated Deal Creation**: Turn Trello cards into HubSpot deals with a single click
- **Customizable Mapping**: Choose which Trello data translates to specific HubSpot deal fields
- **Pipeline Synchronization**: Align Trello lists with HubSpot deal stages
- **Time-Saving Workflow**: Eliminate manual data entry and reduce platform switching

Ideal for sales teams who manage leads in Trello but need to track and report in HubSpot. Our Power-Up bridges the gap between your visual task management and your CRM, ensuring no opportunity slips through the cracks.

Supercharge your sales process and keep your CRM up-to-date without leaving Trello!

# Pricing Structure for Paid Power-Up

Our Power-Up operates on a credit-based system, offering flexibility and value for our users.

## Credit Pricing

- $1 for 100 credits

## Usage

- 1 credit = 1 Card Generation

## Benefits

- Pay-as-you-go model
- Credits never expire
- Flexible for both occasional and power users

## How It Works

1. Purchase credits at $1 for 100 credits
2. Use credits to generate cards as needed
3. Replenish your credit balance when running low

## Custom Solutions

For high-volume users or enterprises, we offer tailored packages. Contact our sales team for more information.

---

Start creating cards today and only pay for what you use!

## Support

If you encounter any problem or have any query, the API Labz team is here to help you. Contact us at info@apilabz.com or schedule a meeting with us.

listing.description:
The Google Drive Power-Up for Trello brings your files and folders to Trello cards. Search Google Drive right from Trello and attach relevant files and folders. See real-time previews and details and click back into Google Drive. It also lets you turn your Trello board into a Google Slides presentation with one click.

- Built in file search lets you attach folders and files from Google Drive to a Trello card on any version of Trello.
- See real-time information and previews for any Google Drive files or folders attached to cards.
- Turn your Trello board into a Google Slides presentation with one click.

listing.name: TeamGantt
listing.description:
The [TeamGantt](https://www.teamgantt.com) Power-Up gives you the ability to view and schedule your cards in a beautiful timeline.

TeamGantt is the popular project scheduling tool used by thousands of customers in over 120 countries.

+ Organize cards from multiple boards into a single, beautiful gantt chart inside Trello
+ Add project dependencies and resourcing to Trello boards
+ Sync dates and completion rates across services automatically
+ Works in all major web browsers


![Gantt Chart](https://trello.teamgantt.com/images/screenshot.gif)
![Card back](https://trello.teamgantt.com/images/card-back.png)


### Two sync modes are available:


+ **Auto Link**
Automatically sync newly created cards and tasks from one Trello board to a single TeamGantt gantt chart. Cards are synced immediately on creation. This is the easiest and most common link type. Best if you want to have all the cards in a single board displayed in a Gantt chart.

![Sync Options](https://trello.teamgantt.com/images/sync-options.png)

+ **Manual Link**
Gives you full control over when and where your cards are synced to TeamGantt. As the name implies, this sync mode requires some manual work. You will need to individually pick which cards you want to display in a timeline. This allows you to pick and choose which cards you want to see in a Gantt chart

  + Send cards from one Trello board to multiple gantt charts
  + Sync cards from multiple Trello boards to a single gantt chart 
  + Cards are not automatically synced on creation, allowing you to finalize a card's details before syncing to TeamGantt
  + Manual Link is more hands on compared to Auto Link, but it gives you the ultimate in flexibility.

### Professional Gantt Charts Loaded With Features:

TeamGantt brings the leading online Gantt chart software to Trello!

![Features](https://trello.teamgantt.com/images/TeamGantt-trello.png)
listing.overview: View your cards in a beautiful timeline with the popular project scheduling tool used by thousands of customers in over 120 countries.
